text: Jeff Henckels (born 30 August 1984) is an archer from Luxembourg. Henckels competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Jeff HenckelsJeff HENCKELS == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian archers Category:Olympians for Luxembourg
